Tina Fey is a hot, hot MILF who is having bed troubles with her incompetent husband Steve Carrell who can't get it up anymore.

In a bid for a little excitement, they drive from Jersey to Manhattan to crash a swanky restaurant without having a reservation. They succeed by pretending to be Harry Osbourne & Mila Kunis. Olivia Munn totally believes it and unfortunately, so do a couple of dirty cops & the Ray Liotta Mafia who want a generic MacGuffin plot device from them.

They then do things which make *completely* no sense one after another and end up meeting a half-naked Mark Wahlberg who Fey flirts with. In revenge, Carrell takes Wahlberg's expensive Audi and completely trashes it.

Finally, they come to their senses and call the cops who then sort things out. The end.
